msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Ah, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Did I keep you waiting?\r\nSorry about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Not at all, I just got here myself.\r\nShall we, then?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "It's all thanks to your sweet talk that\r\nI have these debts now! Own up to it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "H-How is that my fault!?\r\nYou're the one who ordered it all, aren't you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "You said you wouldn't have a good time\r\nunless I ordered champagne and all that..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "And after I order half the menu, you go and\r\nget me banned from the club!? You bitch!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "No! S-Someone help!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "The guy's trying to pin his debts on that\r\nhostess. A sorry and familiar tune..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Huh? I think she's from our club..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Hey, wait."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "What do you think you're doing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Eh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "R-Riona-san...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "This is exactly why I always tell you not to\r\nput so much pressure on your customers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry...\r\nI never imagined he'd do this..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Hey, who the hell are you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "I sincerely apologize if you felt any pressure\r\nto spend money at our club."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "But, in the end, the choice rests with the customer,\r\nand we can't assume responsibility for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "What is this shit?\r\nYou think I'm gonna let a woman lecture me!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Fuck it, I ain't above punching you out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Gah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Listen, I'm not letting you hit her or anyone else\r\nI'm with. See how far you get with me, first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Asshole... I'll destroy you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "I-I'm so sorry!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "There's nothin' to apologize for."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "But... You're right, if I'd followed your advice,\r\nthis never would have happened."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "When I saw the way you never pressured clients\r\ninto buying, I thought you were just a weakling..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "In the hostess business, sales are everything..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "But I see just how wrong I was, now.\r\nYour customers would never sink this low."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Everyone admires you, Riona-san,\r\nand they always leave the club so happy..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "I... want to be just like you.\r\nI don't want to cause any more sadness."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "I'm sure you can pull it off.\r\nAnd I've got your back, all the way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Thank you! From here on, I'm going to be a\r\nmore conscientious hostess! Thank you so much!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Good for you. Looks like you've got another\r\njunior hostess who's willing to listen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Yep. Kiryu-san, thank you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "No prob. But y'know, you should have let me handle\r\nthat. It's a man's job to protect the woman he's with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "You're right, sorry...\r\nI just wanted to rescue that poor girl..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "I understand what you mean, and I like that about\r\nyou. But you've got to lean on others sometimes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "It's not weakness to depend on others.\r\nIn fact, it's proof of your strength."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "You really are the coolest, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Well, what do you say we start over?\r\nYou had somewhere you wanted to go?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Yeah, let's go, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

